des:
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you smart devices - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your LaView products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "LaView" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one LaView account in our "LaView" app;
(3). You need to have some LaView devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “LaView” app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "LaView" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "LaView" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "LaView", and you'll be navigated to LaView login page;
(9). Input your LaView account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa，Show Camera"
“Alexa，Hide the Camera"
“Alexa，Stop the Camera"
